%% Trace: features/02-手機忘記密碼發送OTP + 03-手機忘記密碼完成驗證 + 04-手機忘記密碼重設.feature
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant Ctrl as PasswordRecoveryController
    participant Svc as ForgotPasswordService
    participant OtpSvc as OtpService
    participant SMS as ItSmsGateway
    participant Repo as MemberAuthRepository
    participant OtpRepo as OtpRecordRepository

    %% --- Send OTP ---
    User->>FE: 忘記密碼 → 輸入手機 + Captcha
    FE->>Ctrl: POST /forgot/mobile (mobile, captcha)
    Ctrl->>Svc: requestMobileForgotOtp(mobile)
    Svc->>Repo: findByMobileHash (is_deleted=false)
    Repo-->>Svc: member_auth
    Svc->>OtpSvc: issue(contact=mobile, purpose=FORGOT_PASSWORD, channel=sms)
    OtpSvc->>OtpRepo: insert OtpRecord
    OtpSvc->>SMS: enqueue
    OtpSvc-->>Svc: otp_uuid
    Ctrl-->>FE: 200 {otp_uuid}

    %% --- Verify OTP → issue otp_token ---
    User->>FE: 輸入 OTP
    FE->>Ctrl: POST /forgot/verify-otp (otp_uuid, otp_code)
    Ctrl->>Svc: verifyForgotOtp(otp_uuid, otp_code)
    Svc->>OtpSvc: verify(otp_uuid, otp_code, purpose=FORGOT_PASSWORD)
    OtpSvc-->>Svc: ok (contact_hash)
    Svc->>Svc: createOtpToken(member_auth_id, ttl=wrs_otp_token_expiry_sec)
    Svc-->>Ctrl: otp_token
    Ctrl-->>FE: 200 {otp_token, expires_in}

    %% --- Reset password ---
    User->>FE: 輸入新密碼
    FE->>Ctrl: POST /forgot/reset (otp_token, new_password)
    Ctrl->>Svc: resetMobile(otp_token, new_password)
    Svc->>Svc: consumeOtpToken(otp_token) - 一次性使用
    Svc->>Repo: UPDATE member_auths SET password_hash
    Svc-->>Ctrl: ok
    Ctrl-->>FE: 200 OK
    FE-->>User: 重設成功 → 導向登入
